history.content:
Hello!! I am planning on studying leetcode very intensively to find a really good swe internship for summer 2023. I plan to start applying for a ton of places at the end of the summer. There are about 4 months left until August.

I already have a swe internship for this summer 2022, but I want to try SUPER HARD for a FAANG internship for summer 2023. So that once I graduate in Spring 2024 I'll hopefully have a job offer. My main intentions are to build coding and interview confidence. It's okay if I get rejected to a lot of places, because over time my confidence will improve and I'll be more prepared for applying for a full time job once I graduate.

I'm actually also taking a break this semester and will come back fall 2022, so I have quite a bit of time to dedicate to leetcode. 

I'd love to find someone to do this with ! We could motivate each other and have fun in the process. Please email me if you're interested!! anhar07@berkeley.edu

p.s.
I am really serious about this. I'm not going to give up anymore.
history.subject: Looking for LeetCode Buddy!
